Automation Framework (Day-48 to Day-54)

Objectives
--------------
1. Re-usability
2. Maintainability
3. Readability


Types of Frameworks
--------------
1. Built-in
	E.g. TestNG, JUnit, Cucumber, Robot...

2. Customized (user defined)
	E.g. Modular framework, Data Driven, Keyword Driven, Hybrid Driven...
	

Phases/Stages
--------------
1) Analyzing AUT
	- Number of pages
	- what are all elements / how / type
	- What to automate / what we cannot automate
	
2) Choose test cases for automation
	what is 100% automation - to check all the 100 test cases can be automated
	if 100 test cases --- 90 can be automated, 10 cannot be automated, this is not 100% automation
	
Priorities
1. Sanity test - P1
2. Data driven test cases/re tests - P2
3. Regression test cases - P3
4. Any other cases - P4

3) Design & Development of framework
4) Execution - locally, remotely
5) Maintenance

